title: Watch Ryan Adams Perform “Do You Still Love Me?” on “Corden”
text:
Watch Ryan Adams Perform “Do You Still Love Me?” on “Corden” He’s also selling a signature Prisoner guitar pedal Ryan Adams Photo: Terence Patrick/CBS 
Ryan Adams was a musical guest on last night’s episode of “ Late Late Show With James Corden .” He performed “Do You Still Love Me?” from Prisoner . Watch the performance below. 
Adams has also announced that he’s selling a signature Prisoner guitar pedal in collaboration with Reverb . The JHS VCR “combines volume, chorus, and reverb circuits in one decidedly retro box,” according to a website description. Find out more information about the pedal here . A post shared by Ryan Adams (@misterryanadams) on Feb 22, 2017 at 2:12pm PST Artists In This Story
